It would be better for gasoline prices to increase in a slow, steady,
predictable fashion, with gas tax increases scheduled in advance.
But they must increase!
<p>
Now legislators are calling for expanding the Supreme Court to <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/06/30/markey-bowman-join-climate-coalition-urging-scotus-expansion">undo
its climate attack</a>, in addition to abortion rights and voting rights.

 